{"tid":1183643,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"想大家對六四好有記憶　其實唔難","createTime":"2019-06-03T05:41:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-03T06:38:35.000Z","uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"a7446a4d5b21ee4c9ee19a5b32518251846001d6","tid":1183643,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T05:41:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/cheng.lap.9/posts/10157157493352357\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fcheng.lap.9%2Fposts%2F10157157493352357&d=oOXZKU%2BZRanU2kHQSwewOOr6kk4zB%2BnGw4DSdwpbM%2Bg%3D&h=6dd9ea9a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/cheng.lap.9/posts/10157157493352357</a><br />\n<br />\n其實你想大家對六四好有記憶, 不如拍套「北京大屠殺」電影版, 宣傳影片就用電影 CG, 搵條特技人比架坦克輾到血肉橫飛大聲慘叫, 然後有個軍佬奸笑住「傑傑傑」開槍射爆市民個頭, 再放上 youtube 度做廣告, 保證大家對六四即刻記憶深左啦.<br />\n<br />\n抗日神劇靠呢招去到抗戰打完 70 年都仲可以令人母忘日本侵華, 好有效丫.<br />\n<br />\n驚無人睇咪搵林明禎做主角囉.<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nAdam Leung:<br />\n將d坦克車擬人化、萌化可能仲有效<br />\n<br />\nCheng Lap:<br />\n咁畫 H 本囉, 有條友拎住兩個膠袋, 行過架坦克面前, 坦克就化為美少女壓住條友, 跟住噴到周圍都係.<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nCheng Lap:<br />\nd野無娛樂性搵鬼睇咩<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nKevin Pao:<br />\n點解唔搵雷凱欣呢？<br />\n講到有爆炸性又要血肉橫飛，邊個夠佢出名？<br />\n<br />\nCheng Lap:<br />\n好主意, 就搵雷凱欣<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nAndy On:<br />\n然後拍續集，64復仇者聯盟，搵主角雙手撕開坦克<br />\n<br />\nCheng Lap:<br />\n北京又屠殺<br />\n<br />\nCheng Lap:<br />\n戴埋頭盔, 話套野純屬虛構, 入面唔叫解放軍, 叫解決軍囉, 咁唔叫中華人民共和國, 中華百姓共和國囉, 唔叫鄧小平, 叫丁大丙, 李鵬都唔叫李鵬, 搵隻雕兄代替.<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nLiana Au:<br />\n要有愛情元素，例如鐵達尼<br />\n<br />\n Cheng Lap:<br />\n「如果你輾死 1000 個反革命份子證明你是個愛國而有事業心的男人求婚我就和你結婚」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n賀維斯:<br />\n玩時空&quot;橋&quot;囉，主角係腐女一名<br />\n<br />\nCheng Lap:<br />\n因為寫 BL 小說被人引渡返大陸打靶, 打靶果一下就穿越返左去 1989 年<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nMichael Y. H. Chiu: 會被禁播<br />\n<br />\nCheng Lap: pornhub"},{"pid":"9ded1e06a9efefdb49a2d8ae77f6d4b6df699686","tid":1183643,"uid":226955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T06:26:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e9f1c6ba6d0c1f454b9dfeb9ff508d57e02d88a","tid":1183643,"uid":6674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T06:27:35.000Z","msg":"CLS<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25d97a96be63062c66b3218f4ad74823dff77a60","tid":1183643,"uid":47714,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T06:29:19.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/cheng.lap.9/posts/10157156804207357\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fcheng.lap.9%2Fposts%2F10157156804207357&d=oOXZKU%2BZRanU2kHQSwewOOr6kk4zB%2BnGw4DSdwpbM%2Bg%3D&h=d5347f6c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/cheng.lap.9/posts/10157156804207357</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GJDo8qn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGJDo8qn.png&h=22515fd8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nAlex Hon:<br />\n本身已經唔教<br />\n支NA會剩係識圍爐<br />\n何況華人教科書根本係神話小說<br />\n將拳民恐怖襲擊西方人兼大清向萬國宣戰<br />\n解釋成八國聯軍。<br />\n<br />\nCheng Lap:<br />\n不需要教科書，像我都做漫畫、遊戲之類，他們也可以做，但他們不做。<br />\n<br />\nAlex Hon:<br />\n艦娘╭(╯3╰)╮<br />\nFGO真香<br />\n<br />\n所以立爺先係啱,佢哋......<br />\n年年悲情拜山<br />\n<br />\nCheng Lap:<br />\n講到咩毋忘，佢地自己圍爐有咩用"},{"pid":"b2df74ab837a61d118ca12502a620437799a8c57","tid":1183643,"uid":47714,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T06:36:22.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://twitter.com/LungZenoOpen/status/1032324105196826625\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FLungZenoOpen%2Fstatus%2F1032324105196826625&d=oOXZKU%2BZRanU2kHQSwewOOr6kk4zB%2BnGw4DSdwpbM%2Bg%3D&h=da863c74\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FLungZenoOpen%2Fstatus%2F1032324105196826625&h=c1776ad4\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitt